This demo requires TCC (Tiny C Compiler, see http://bellard.org/tcc/) installed.

Visit http://bellard.org/tcc/ or install TCC by another way.

Do not forget to add path to "tcc" tool to your PATH environment variable.

This is the classic AI benchmark problem. See sample/santa_fe_ant_trial/README for details.

Run 
./animate_c.rb winner.c ant_animate.c
to see the animation of the winner.c phenotype.

sample/ant_trail_tcc/attr_grammar/ subdir contains the attribute grammar experiment:
Restricting node expansion during the genotype-phenotype mapping ensures the functions
fn1() .. fn3() are properly defined before they are used.
See semantic.yaml for attributes description.

